(10979, 827, 'additional_blocks_4_text', 'Reputable <a href=\"/nzd-casinos/\">online casino with NZ dollars</a> offers their clients tools to encourage responsible gambling. Yet, most tools are not automatic, and you\'ll have to be reasonable with gambling. Meaning, you have to activate mechanisms to restrain yourself on purpose. Though online casinos can remind you when you\'ve crossed some limits, it\'s up to you to decide to cool off for a bit.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><b>Use free/paid gambling blockers.</b>\r\nRegister to the services of <a href=\"https://betblocker.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Betblocker</a> and <a href=\"https://gamban.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gamban</a> to have the chance to exclude yourself from gambling for a period of your choice. Such blocking software allows players to change the settings of their browsers. Meaning, once they install the software, it\'ll start banning all gambling websites.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Set Time-Outs.</b>\r\nResponsible NZ gambling includes tools such as specifying gamble session lengths. This way, you\'ll keep track of the time spent on gambling and won\'t lose. Or you can take a break that can last from 24 hours to several months. In this period, gamblers cannot log in to their account.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Set Deposit Limits.</b>\r\nThis strategy will help you keep within the projected budget limits. The good thing is that you can set the limits on a daily, weekly, or monthly level. If you know you have limits, it becomes easier to give up at the right time. Most NZ operators grant this possibility.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Set Loss Limits.</b>\r\nSelf-limitation methods are one of the most efficient to control your gambling activities. You have options to put a cap on the losses of a specific game or the entire platform. In short, setting a strict budget before commencing will help you gamble in a sensible and restrictive way.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Unsubscribe from e-mail newsletters.</b>\r\nThis is an excellent method to prevent possible gambling problems in the future. Newsletters of New Zealand gambling brands offer promotions, bonuses, coupon codes, and many attractive deals. If you ban them, you\'ll save yourself from having to resist the immediate temptation to join a game.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Contact customer support to find the best usage ways.</b>\r\nIf the problem is serious, you might have to seek professional support. You can also seek upfront advice on the most reasonable ways to gamble. There are various options that NZ players have at disposal. Most of them are free and offer 24/7 support online.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
