(10996, 827, '_additional_blocks_5_casino_taxonomy', 'field_5ce26afd55a81'),
(10997, 827, 'additional_blocks_5_text', 'Responsible Kiwi iGaming companies never make money on players suffering from gambling addiction. Helping Kiwi players stay in control is what they consider a top priority. The following features must be an essential tool for every online casino operator. They ensure the wellbeing of players and highlight the operator’s dedication too.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><b>Active license.</b>\r\nAlways play at licensed casinos since they must obey the laws and rules of governing bodies. Be aware of <a href=\"/new-casinos/\">new online casino sites</a> and check whether they have a valid gambling license. Licenses bind online casinos to protect their customers. They also have to introduce fair play protocols.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Self-Exclusion.</b>\r\nVerified online casinos must provide clients with self-exclusion tools. They must also make sure gamblers know this possibility. This option is mandatory with the opportunity to voluntarily self-exclude. Alternatively, you can delete the account forever. Gambling platforms must deter players when they exceed the loss limits within a specific timeframe.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Test on Gambling Addiction.</b>\r\nOnline casinos and support organizations offer <a href=\"https://www.psycom.net/gambling-addiction-test/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">fast self-assessment tests</a>. This way, they allow players to check their condition. The assessment will detect if you have gambling issues and underline the seriousness of the problem. This facility will inform you if you have to take restrictive measures, too.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
