(11033, 827, 'additional_blocks_7_text', 'Getting over a bad gambling habit is not an easy path to take. You need a lot of support and advice along the way to stay true to your intentions. Being addicted to gambling is tough but beatable. Support organizations can help you endure in moments of weakness. Plus, top Kiwi online casinos cooperate with them regularly.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.gamblinghelpline.co.nz/Home_452.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gambling Helpline</a> is a widely available support network for New Zealand players. It\'s a national free-phone service that operates 24/7. The helpline offers various services and provides essential gambling information. The advice they provide is personalized, and the forum accepts anonymous users.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.choicenotchance.org.nz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Choice Not Chance</a> is a program of the NZ Health Promotion Agency. Its purpose is to raise awareness related to the harms of addictive gambling. Targeted strategies include a free gambling test. Can you beat or cheat a pokie machine is one of the techniques to destimulate online gambling.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.pgf.nz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Problem Gambling Foundation</a> offers counsellors trained to help. The organization provides professional advice for both gamblers and people affected by gambling. Support groups further encourage members to resist the urge of one more game. They offer great relief and help players get their lives back to normal.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
