(3016226, 1501370, 'additional_blocks_8_text', 'Has your debt reached a point that you find it impossible to manage? The only thing you need to do is seek help. There are plenty of organizations that offer debt management services. Debt advice platforms may present you with the full range of payment options. Another aspect they assist with is surviving the aggressive money-recuperation tactics of creditors.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.insolvency.govt.nz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Insolvency and Trustee Service</a> is part of the Ministry of Business, Innovation, and Employment. They offer various insolvency options depending on the amount you owe. DRO or Debt Repayment Order is the best insolvency option for amounts below $50,000. The service provides supervisors both for individuals and companies.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.debtfix.co.nz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Debtfix</a> intends to act as a lifesaver of people drowning in debts. They provide relief, advice on how to manage debts, and plausible solutions. The approach towards each money problem is personalized, and solutions are tailored to suit the needs of troubled clients. The guidance eliminates resorting to bankruptcy.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.capnz.org/get-help/debt-help\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CAP Debt Help</a> offers long-term debt counselling in cases of severe debts and money problems. Use their debt management plans and get supported by the CAP team. Plus, they negotiate with creditors on your behalf. After a phone call, a caseworker will offer you a workable repayment plan.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
(3016227, 1501370, '_additional_blocks_8_text', 'field_6049f573dbb7b'),
