e case with all countries where online gambling is popular. If you’re not from New Zealand and you come from a non-Mastercard country, you won’t be able to use this method.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Withdrawals can take up to 5 days</b>. There are payment methods and companies that offer a faster withdrawal time than Mastercard. Usually, Mastercard withdrawal casino process can take up to 5 days, while some platforms offer cashouts in under 24 hours. If fast payouts are your priority, search for <a href=\"/fast-payout-casinos/\">instant withdrawal online casino</a> where you can deposit with Mastercard and get cash using a fast method.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
