s Kiwis and Aussies since this method is available to them only. Hence, players can expect bonuses and game menus tailored to suit their different taste.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><strong>Apple Pay</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Do you own an Apple device, like, for example, an iPhone or an iPad? Then, Apple Pay casinos are the right pick for you. These gambling destinations support both mobile play and Apple Pay deposits. Meaning, you can easily top up your casino account and stay protected by the impressive Apple Touch ID.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><strong>Paysafecard</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Do you want anonymous cash transfers? Would you prefer not to enter credit card details while making a casino deposit? Well, all <a href=\"/paysafe-casinos/\">Paysafe casinos</a> are an excellent option for you. Paysafe is a prepaid voucher, which is perfect for secure, instant, and small casino payments. Moreover, using Paysafecard is free of charge and incredibly convenient.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><strong>PayPal</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Being the world’s most commonly used e-wallet, PayPal is a popular mobile casino payment method too. Making a deposit with <a href=\"/paypal-casinos/\">casino sites accepting PayPal</a> provide with many benefits for Kiwis. For example, such transfers are processed instantly and often come without any processing fees. Plus, PayPal payments are 100% secure and keep credit card details outside casino servers.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>'),
